text = "Controls:
- P1 Move: WASD | Confirm: E | End Turn: Q
- P2 Move: IJKL | Confirm: O | End Turn: U

Current Features:
- Tile highlight: valid / invalid / entity / self
- Move to empty tiles with pathing
- Interact/attack on entity (plays AttackCam)
- Camera follows party centroid
- Debug grid overlay
- Dice sandbox: d4/d6/d8/d10/d12/d20 + custom formula

Toggles:
- F1: Debug Info
- F2: Dice Sandbox
- F3: Debug Grid"

